Administrative defects are recorded to indicate quality issues with the maintenance tracking data. They do not reflect actual defects with the aircraft and are not added to the AC Journey Log. Typically, they are created when a component BOM has missing components where there is no history of the component ever being installed - a situation that can occur when lines are first added to the BOM but not populated with component data.
Is the defect administrative? If selected, the defect will not be added to the AC Journey log.
